column1: Write a JUnit test method for the Java method described below. The test method should have proper and relevant assert statements and avoid repetition of assert statements.

Method: visitUsingCustomHandler
Description: /**
* This is called to visit an object using a custom handler
*
* @return true if a custom handler exists, false otherwise
*/

Method: visitFieldUsingCustomHandler
Description: /**
* This is called to visit a field of the current object using a custom
* handler
*/

Method: accept
Description: /**
* Navigate all the fields of the specified object. If a field is null, it
* does not get visited.
*/
